<A>__{a non conformist chapel. empty, except for one figure, a woman laying out music on the organ rack in the front of the chapel. the camera moves in on her, and as she turns on her way to the hymn board, we see that she is mrs. drayton. at the hymn board, she slips into it a series of hymn numbers.}
